{"tid":146432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞禁止北韓人離境","createTime":"2017-03-07T05:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T09:59:12.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91e02cd955a61b584b129395ee99f791afa5e2c9","tid":146432,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"大馬副首相兼內政部長阿末扎希（Ahmad Zahid Hamidi）隨即也宣佈，即時禁駐當地大使館的工作人員、官員等人離開大馬，理由是有使館人員涉及謀殺案。他會根據《維也納外交關係公約》，協助在朝鮮被禁止出境的大馬人。他還說，首相納吉將在本週五的內閣會議上，討論是否關閉在平壤的大馬駐北韓大使館。外交部初步相信目前有11名大馬人在北韓，包括三名使館人員、兩名聯合國職員及六名親屬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170307/56394996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170307%2F56394996&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=0be990b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170307%2F56394996&h=96b63414\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170307/56394996</a>"},{"pid":"9601ab0b97ba9deeb6823518c40d077c559a5412","tid":146432,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"金正恩理得班人死<br />\n班北韓人都唔想番去"},{"pid":"bcd75e763ba8d16c9a5c6947aa5a6999ea4a69b7","tid":146432,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"獎定罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383b075a3fea1ebdd3880d898b3d0787e0e03fdd","tid":146432,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"lm睇北韓處決外交官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8454e46af39775788987768229f429be2f2c3e","tid":146432,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"